---
title: Korean-Inspired Beef Burger with Pickled Veggies and Gochujang Mayo
description: The ever-popular Korean rice bowl has been re-imagined as a delicious burger and we are egg-cited! (Pun intended!) But seriously, the egg on top makes all the difference!
